{"type": "article", "id": 51159, "title": "五种植物的细节，都藏在这五把天鹅绒椅子里｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-15T23:35:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48480, "name": "secolo XXI"}, {"id": 16335, "name": "Plumen"}, {"id": 33632, "name": "Shigeki Yamamoto"}, {"id": 48481, "name": "Pia Wüstenburg"}, {"id": 48482, "name": "Ammar Kalo"}, {"id": 48483, "name": "Daniel Becker"}, {"id": 24005, "name": "Andreas Engesvik"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 86, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180316012627FqroNKQVAycneBWR.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Agnes chair by Andreas Engesvik </h3><p>挪威设计师 Andreas Engesvik 将柔软的面料与斜倚的木质框架结合在一起，为瑞典设计品牌 Ire 设计了一把名为 Agnes 的休闲椅。他的目标是创造一个适合城市公寓和夏日别墅的椅子，因此形状需要那种非正式、放松的感觉，就像一个“温柔、温暖的人”。</p><p>Agnes 椅子的框架由斯堪的纳维亚木材制成，并与瑞典南部的手工艺人团队合作生产。然后设计师将地毯般的皮革或纺织品材料罩在木框上，让椅子呈现出更加放松的氛围。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012716Uva0Smgs3WNjyECR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.796108\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012715mWJ3zEihGO7aZs0n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012717MbXeThW1lO5NDVsc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.847716\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012717u78pvKIcXqFkBhwT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.840102\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Willow &amp; Wilma by Daniel Becker</h3><p>英国灯具品牌 Plumen 请来设计师 Daniel Becker，推出 Willow 与 Wilma 两款新产品，作为 LED 灯丝系列的延伸。灵活小巧的 LED 灯丝带组成形似精美花冠的灯丝，位于灯泡中心处。灯泡外壳完全采用手工吹制，将精致的灯丝包裹在其中，每盏吊灯还具有手工绘制的金色玻璃外观。</p><p>据称两款灯泡的灵感来源于托马斯·爱迪生的白炽灯，使用者可以将其多个搭配或作为吊灯使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012752zA0OmgvqIH1XVJbF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.196822\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012752pC3t4wNSbBkH2Ed7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.353301\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803160127534rLm9FpEeQdy2P50.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.211491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803160127532e9lG56oIfEAXinR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.525672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012753XB2qE0A813JUWSnf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803160127573CpQJfSD0zqkrl8h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.392421\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Fikra Tables by Ammar Kalo</h3><p>设计师 Ammar Kalo 最新推出的这一系列 Fikra 桌，展示了天然材料和人造材料之间的完美平衡，用再生橡胶碎屑强化视觉层面的沉重感。</p><p>这一系列作品是受阿联酋多用途空间 Fikra Campus 委托而设计，这个空间内有联合办公场所、咖啡馆、设计图书馆以及画廊，每个桌子都专门为特定用途和位置而设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803160128223rTv6R97EaVL1NqK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012822cMqbxzWDK01uhpRl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012822b73B28TtphYsHJfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012823cHWaXLnf5d6vUJDw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012823sfpGtvjumrgneOdw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/ammar-kalo-oak-rubber-table-fikra-03-15-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Giardino Botanico Collection from secolo XXI</h3><p>这是伦敦品牌 secolo XXI 推出的首个系列产品，按照品牌方的说法，他们想带来的不仅是新鲜的产品，而且是令人兴奋的，并要在接下来的时间内持续保持优雅。</p><p>Giardino Botanico 系列由 5 把天鹅绒饰面的椅子组成，参与设计的是伦敦艺术设计工作室 Artefatto。这一系列将在 4 月的米兰设计周上亮相，与天鹅绒饰面颜色相呼应的是植物造型的靠背，包括雏菊、百合、常春藤、茉莉和冬青。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012900kXOAHWVgai1K90En.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012901IoevRSxtFH93fpK1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012901BUMewg3zl47u8m1W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012902nmOIsWNXAhvcr8gC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.252222\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/secolo-xxi-giardino-botanico-03-14-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>STACKING VESSELS by Pia Wüstenburg</h3><p>Pia Wüstenburg 出生于德国，有过在英国留学的经历，又曾在芬兰生活过，她想将这些不同地域之间的文化影响力的差异植入自己的设计中。2011 年在伦敦皇家艺术学院毕业后，她结合木雕、玻璃和金属材料，发展出五个形态各异的器皿，被称为 Stacking Vessels 系列，期待为当代家居环境创造出仪式感，也是她关于不同材料的审美对比，手工艺与工业生产的对比，新旧材料的对比的持续探索。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012948rJKFkX9EmSsjut8d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012949rmBdW1ASM94Kx5HR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012949k3X4EpFHhjn2Su9o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012950S8OcKNmCpE2tPy9k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012950OBPE4y67hQtmFegU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316012951tSOsfrdM54ckHAL2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/german-finnish-designer-pia-wustenburg-seeking-solitude-life-work-contrast/design_milk_utopia_and_utility_09/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pia Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Play Cabinet 2017 by Shigeki Yamamoto</h3><p>柏林设计师 Shigeki Yamamoto 设计的这款 Play Cabinet 2017，是其儿童积木系列中的最新作品。</p><p>这一系列的灵感都是来自玩耍积木的童年回忆，橱柜由多孔木条组成，带有插头和螺丝连接，2016 年推出的 Play Sideboard 餐具柜也使用了这种方式。</p><p><a href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-childhood-toy-inspired-cabinet-by-shigeki-yamamoto/playful-cabinet-shigeki-yamamoto-13/\" rel=\"nofollow\">设计师说</a>：“我一直都想要利用这种技术创造更加复杂的结构，Play Cabinet 代表着现在我探索之旅的巅峰，然而这场探索还远远没有结束。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316013158pKLmWJCsornzvIyO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316013158b0wBsdCu9D8rnXPy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.958594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803160131599OXer2NhimTDdWIS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316013200WfBeQzV8D7gAZyEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316013201N1oCRv0GxuJwmhXj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180316013201xahcl275DBfFE8TH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-childhood-toy-inspired-cabinet-by-shigeki-yamamoto/playful-cabinet-shigeki-yamamoto-13/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}